========================================================================
                         I. Instructions
========================================================================
1. Execute the .jar file to start the game.
2. Chose the number of colors to match.
3. Click on a square to show its color, then on another square. If the
   colors of the two squares match, those squares stay activated.
4. When you've matched all the colors, you win!
